{"tid":1480910,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日818遊行一定要Loop聖詩！","createTime":"2019-08-17T13:27:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T05:52:43.000Z","uid":194553,"like":103,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"ebb499a6f274883000a5c39e7686894712db3a9f","tid":1480910,"uid":194553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:27:02.000Z","msg":"最近大家好似已經唔記得左Sing Hallelujah to the Lord哩首歌<br />\n<br />\n但我想提醒返咁多位，聽日我地好應該再loop返E首歌，<span style=\"color: green;\">因為係一個非法但和平既集會遊行入面唱宗教歌曲係有4大好處</span>：<br />\n<br />\n1.<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 將非法既遊行集會合法化</span></span><br />\n因為係香港宗教類型既集會係唔需要申請，而聽日818係維園外既遊行其實算係非法，但假如長期有人唱住隻歌，我地就可以改變個集會既定性<br />\n<br />\n2. 有人會講：反正警犬都唔跟規舉做野，唱聖詩佢都唔會當你地合法聚會嫁啦。E個PT某程度都無錯，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">但重點係持續唱聖詩係一定有助於遊行人士免受刑責風險</span></span>，因為假如狗最後真係出催淚彈然後濫捕和平既示威者，最後落唔落charge係律政處，如果有好多片影到係有人長期唱緊詩歌，就會令聽日遊行比較容易argue到成一個大型宗教既集會，變相就好似差佬混入示威者之後，法庭會因為示威者既過激行為唔知係唔係由差佬做，疑點利益歸於被告既情況下 --&gt; 最終告唔入 OR 因為知道大機會輸所以索性唔告<br />\n<br />\n3. 如果狗係大家和平唱聖詩既時候，繼續放催淚彈or施暴既話，我地又會多左文宣題材，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">而且d片段仲可以直接target海外既宗教界別</span></span><br />\n<br />\n4. <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">短暫紓緩大家同警犬之間既仇恨情緒</span></span><br />\n雖然我知大家見到警犬811同之前既惡行仲好嬲，但我地要記住聽日既集會策略上暫時既共識係係由頭到尾盡量和理非，所以如果個環境長期充滿左peaceful既詩歌，相信會令雙方既情緒都會較為平和、冷靜，咁樣除左會減少雙方爆發衝突既情況，亦可以令果D想無事生非既內鬼冇咁容易入手<br />\n<br />\n所以呼籲各位<span style=\"color: green;\">愛主既耶青</span>準時空群出動！讓讚美主既詩句傳遍金鐘銅鑼灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n認同既話請大家正評幫推！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3592ef3900c64208f1ef2caa1dbc7d521dcf424","tid":1480910,"uid":186845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:28:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bc7e45251823bfe25434ff9d6df16411d55d6e6","tid":1480910,"uid":194553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:30:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"660e5537eedee3fb8bbfd6faba71fce344b28a35","tid":1480910,"uid":35870,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:31:42.000Z","msg":"其實想同大定推介下呢首<br />\nBattle Hymn of the Republic <br />\n基督徒作戰嘅歌<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/q2LZ9cVRkDw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fq2LZ9cVRkDw&d=9fV5YN%2BdLeg0vJDpI0pnmpq%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=e43d205b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/q2LZ9cVRkDw</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nGlory! Glory! Hallelujah! Glory! Glory! Hallelujah!<br />\nGlory! Glory! Hallelujah! His truth is marching on.<br />\n<br />\nAs He died to make men holy, let us die to make men free;<br />\nWhile God is marching on."},{"pid":"cb8ba558ae5181a1c8d500f80561b5af8f572772","tid":1480910,"uid":155487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:32:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0cdc12e37de75806c85e6c05ec7e3764f9d9999e","tid":1480910,"uid":155487,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:32:27.000Z","msg":"推 好撚耐冇唱喇 好想唱歌"},{"pid":"d9eb4e69eb86aa0f4e07b3222be6a798597a09d2","tid":1480910,"uid":194553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:38:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ea9e948349262c43c7af1ee73056a44882ab8b14","tid":1480910,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:39:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">「Join us or Burn with us」<br />\n「對抗暴政，否則攬炒」</span>"},{"pid":"534a692ac62d3d0f06b8c8c6e4a88dc5ef07f169","tid":1480910,"uid":289846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ebb499a6f274883000a5c39e7686894712db3a9f